&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate combines strong business development experience, operational leadership, stakeholder management, and a deep understanding of the LATAM market. This role is similar in scope to a senior cross-functional leadership position, but with a clear regional focus on Argentina and Latin America.&lt;/p&gt;
