&lt;li&gt;Lead corporate development initiatives across Argentina and LATAM.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain relationships with local partners, universities, institutions, government bodies, investors, and business communities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify new business opportunities, strategic partnerships, and market expansion opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent the company in the region and act as the key senior point of contact for local stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the development and execution of the regional growth strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with global leadership across business, finance, legal, HR, operations, and product teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help establish and scale local operations, processes, and teams where needed.&lt;/li&gt;
